//
// Calypso : CT2000 card structures
//
//

/*
**	Les structures CT2000 gérées sont les suivantes :
**____________________________________________________________________
**
**  Architecture standard :
**
**										LID		SID			NbRec
**										-----	--------	----
**		MF								$3F00	 -			13
**		|-- Keys						$0018	 -			5
**		|-- PIN							$0000	 -			1
**		|-- ICC							$0002	$02			1
**		|-- ID Carte					$0003	$03			1
**		|-- ID Générale					$0004	$04			5
**		|-- DOFOCO						$2000	 -			28
**		|	|-- Keys					$2018	 -			5
**		|	|-- ID Transport			$2070	$01			1
**		|	|-- Environement			$2001	$07			1
**		|	|-- Porteur					$2002	$1B			1
**		|	|-- Liste Spécial evt		$2003	$1C			1
**		|	|-- Spécial evt				$2040	$1D			3
**		|	|-- Journal transport		$2010	$08			6
**		|	|-- Liste contrats			$2050	$1E			1
**		|	|-- O/D Memory				$2030	$06			-
**		|	|-- Contrats				$2020	$09			8
**		|	|-- Compteurs				$2069	$19			1		(9 compteurs de 3 octets)
**		|	|-- Simulated counter 1		$202A	$0A			-
**		|	|-- Simulated counter 2		$202B	$0B			-
**		|	|-- Simulated counter 3		$202C	$0C			-
**		|	|-- Simulated counter 4		$202D	$0D			-
**		|	|-- Simulated counter 5		$202E	$0E			-
**		|	|-- Simulated counter 6		$202F	$0F			-
**		|	|-- Simulated counter 7		$2060	$10			-
**		|	|-- Simulated counter 8		$2061	$11			-
**		|	|-- Simulated counter 9		$2062	$12			-
**		|
**		|-- GTML						$2100	 -			18
**		|	|-- Keys					$2118	 -			5
**		|	|-- Environement			$2101	$15			1
**		|	|-- Events Log				$2110	$16			3
**		|	|-- Contracts				$2120	$18			4
**		|	|-- Contracts List			$2150	$1A			1
**		|	|-- All counter				$2169	$17			1		(9 compteurs de 3 octets)
**		|	|-- Special events			$2140	$05			1
**		|	|-- Free Access				$2170	 -			2
**		|
**		|-- MPP1-2						$3i00	 -			24
**		|	|-- Keys					$3i18	 -			5
**		|	|-- Counters				$3i13	$13-$14		1
**		|	|-- Contracts				$3i20	 -			6
**		|	|-- Misc					$3i41	 -			6
**		|	|-- Log						$3i15	 -			6
**		|
**		|-- MPP3-6						$3i00	 -			16
**			|-- Keys					$3i18	 -			5
**			|-- Misc					$3i42	 -			11
**	
**____________________________________________________________________	
**
**  Architecture SemurVal :
**
**										LID		SID			NbRec
**										-----	--------	----
**		MF								$3F00	 -			13
**		|-- Keys						$0018	 -			4
**		|-- PIN							$0000	 -			1
**		|-- ICC							$0002	$02			1
**		|-- Infos Transcarte			$0001	$01			1
**		|-- Validité					$0003	$03			1
**		|-- ID Générale					$0004	$04			5
**		|-- SEMURVAL					$4100	 -			16
**		|	|-- Keys					$4118	 -			4
**		|	|-- Identification			$4101	$05			2
**		|	|-- Habilitation			$4102	$07			1
**		|	|-- Paramètres TPV/TPVS		$4103	$08			7
**		|	|-- Paramètres Contrôleur	$4104	$09			1
**		|	|-- Paramètre Valideur		$4105	$13			1
**	
**
*/

